from dataiku.scenario import Scenario

client = dataiku.api_client()
scenario = Scenario()
project = client.get_project("DKU_CHURN")

#Doesn't matter that we use the channel id "slack-"

sender = scenario.get_message_sender(channel_id="YOUR MESSAGE CHANNEL ID")

message =  "You have a new ticket %s from %s, %s\n> *<%s|%s>* \n\n"

sender.send(
    username="your user name",
    message=message,
    mode="WEBHOOK",
    webhookUrl='YOUR WEBHOOK URL',
    useGlobalChannel=False
